Two weeks on from @EFDevcon Buenos Aires and it's clear that ENS is becoming core infrastructure for Ethereum's next phase.

In case you missed the action, here are the ways ENS is meeting demand for L2 identities, agents, decentralized websites, and more. üßµ 
Every Devconnect attendee was eligible to receive a worldfair.eth subname through the event app, with avatars, addresses, and social metadata.

